<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Bruce Aylward</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/2177?language=en' lang='en'>
Humanity vs. Ebola. How we could win a terrifying war
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
